## 八、CSS Override 参考（el-overrides.css）

```css
/* ===== DatePicker Panel ===== */
.el-picker__popper .el-picker-panel {
  border-radius: 6px;
  box-shadow: 0 10px 10px 0 rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.08);
}

/* Month & Year header */
.el-date-picker__header-label {
  font-size: 14px;
  color: #5e5873;
  font-weight: 500;
}
.el-date-picker__header-label + .el-date-picker__header-label {
  color: #6e6b7b;
  font-weight: 400;
}

/* Weekday header */
.el-date-table th {
  font-size: 12px;
  color: #6e6b7b;
  font-weight: 400;
}

/* Day cell */
.el-date-table td .el-date-table-cell {
  width: 36px;
  height: 36px;
}

.el-date-table td .el-date-table-cell__text {
  width: 36px;
  height: 36px;
  line-height: 36px;
  border-radius: 18px;
  font-size: 14px;
  color: #6e6b7b;
}

/* Hover */
.el-date-table td:not(.disabled):hover .el-date-table-cell__text {
  background: rgba(var(--pcv-brand-rgb), 0.15);
  color: #6e6b7b;
}

/* Today — filled brand circle */
.el-date-table td.today .el-date-table-cell__text {
  background: var(--pcv-brand);
  color: #ffffff;
  border-radius: 18px;
}

/* Selected */
.el-date-table td.current:not(.disabled) .el-date-table-cell__text {
  background: var(--pcv-brand);
  color: #ffffff;
  border-radius: 18px;
}

/* Range in-between */
.el-date-table td.in-range .el-date-table-cell {
  background: rgba(var(--pcv-brand-rgb), 0.15);
}

/* Disabled */
.el-date-table td.disabled .el-date-table-cell__text {
  color: #b9b9c3;
  cursor: not-allowed;
}

/* Today footer link */
.el-picker-panel__footer .el-button--text {
  color: var(--pcv-brand);
  font-weight: 500;
  font-size: 14px;
}
```

